Octociz/Brix arrived at the battlefield. They immediatly knew what 
was needed.

"Octociz Maximize!"

This was the very first time they had used this body to go to Beast 
Mode. It was solid and strong, with two rocket launchers and his 
horns could be used to grapple things. His scanners said that the bot 
he had been talking with at the CF was coming. Good, all the help he 
can get.

Octociz was about to open fire, believing he was all alone. Then out 
of the corner of his eye he saw two bots(Rex and Firearm)who appeared 
to be Maximals. He was about to run to them, when Brix spoke up

Octociz, let me handle it. I'm more of the warrior.

But, Bronco could come back if you get angry enough

I have to test it eventually.

Octociz relinquished control to Brix, who started running towards the 
two bots. Careful to avoid fire, he finally reached them.

"Hello, my name is Brix, and I heard the transmission. Did the bot 
make it?"
